third coconut you bring down.

603
01:29:45,880 --> 01:29:47,540
- Yes or no?
- Ok.

604
01:29:54,850 --> 01:29:56,720
Watch your head. Dude.

605
01:29:57,160 --> 01:29:58,490
Send them down.

606
01:30:00,020 --> 01:30:02,120
Come on, I'll catch them down here

607
