642
01:34:54,490 --> 01:34:56,080
- Thanks
- You're welcome.

643
01:34:57,290 --> 01:34:59,780
- I'll show you the rest of the motel.
- Ok.

644
01:34:59,960 --> 01:35:01,120
- After you
- Thanks

645
01:35:04,100 --> 01:35:05,460
