647
01:35:09,130 --> 01:35:10,620
My name is Sebastian

648
01:35:10,800 --> 01:35:13,430
I'm in charge of my uncle's motel.

649
01:35:13,600 --> 01:35:15,540
- What's your name?
- Rosa

650
